---

Notes specific to this project:

- Lawful property owners who are living private individuals are minimized
  or pseudonymized in all published material per CLAUDE.md's privacy rule.
  Named occupation officials, judges, and beneficiaries acting in an
  official capacity are not minimized and are documented for accountability
  purposes.
- The raw evidence store (data/) is not part of this repository and is not
  covered by this license; it is retained privately under chain-of-custody
  rules described in CLAUDE.md.
- Source code under src/ and scripts/ is provided as part of this same
  CC BY 4.0 license; if you require a separate permissive code license
  (e.g. MIT) for reuse of the pipeline itself, contact the author.
